    <h1 class="web__item-header">Full stack node.js app</h1>
    <p class="web__item-text award">You can see the app live <a target="_blank" href="http://node.rossfenrick.com/">here</a> and the source code on my <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/rossfenrick/full-stack-node-app">GitHub</a>.</p>
    <div class="web__item-monitor">
      <img src="../../img/monitor-node.png" alt=""class="monitor__web-item">
